[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     49[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   # This is realistic: historical data rarely contains unsafe actions.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     50[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   # The safety constraint layer (Step 4) exists as defense-in-depth:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     51[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   # the policy might extrapolate to unsafe actions for unseen states.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     52[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   ```
